      "acceptanceCriteria": "Order-of-accuracy verification using manufactured solutions for the turbulence and scalar transport equations relevant to hemolysis prediction.",
      "rationale": "Code verification limited to laminar benchmark cases; no manufactured-solution verification performed for the SST k-omega turbulence model or the hemolysis scalar transport equation. Achieved level 2 against required level 4."
    },
    {
